TỔNG KẾT PHẦN HỌC
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  • Security Basics
      • Threat & Risk Assessment, Detection & Prevention
      • Focus areas: Network, System, Data, Cloud
      • Attacks: DoS/DDoS, Man-in-the-Middle, Malware, Internal

  • Network Security
      • Reduce services, local firewall, encryption
      • Tools: firewall-cmd/ufw, ss/ps/lsof, scp/ssh/rsync, nmap, Wireshark

  • System Security
      • Kernel: Patches, module signing, GRUB password
      • Application: Update, disable unused, dedicated users
      • File System: Partitions, mount options, AIDE
      • Authentication: SSH keys, strong passwords, limit sudo

  • Data Security
      • Disk/Partition/File/Container Encryption
      • dm-crypt, LUKS, cryptsetup, GPG
      • Offsite backups

  • Cloud Security
      • IAM (Identity, Authentication, Authorization)
      • Data Security (at rest, in transit, key management)
      • Network Security (VPC, perimeter, security groups)
      • Compute-based Security
      • Application Security (microservices, serverless, APIs)
      • Monitoring & Policy (alerting, auditing, incident response)


KẾT LUẬN
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Phần Security Fundamentals chiếm 16% kỳ thi, bao quát từ basics đến cloud. 

  Áp dụng best practices, tools và monitoring là chìa khóa bảo mật toàn diện.


